modules.description: Provides functions to parse and generate JSON from and to string values, simplifying input and output operations. Works with basic string data and JSON-encoded data structures. Ideal for scripting tasks that require quick JSON manipulation without complex setup.

Converts a stream of strings into a stream of JSON values, expecting the input to be an open JSON array. Processes each JSON document as it becomes available, ensuring proper closure of the top-level array. Useful for handling continuous JSON data feeds in asynchronous I/O operations.
